mappings.name: Returns a list of hotels matching a given keyword.

cityName.description: The name of the city to which the location belongs to.

countryCode.description: The countrycode to which the location belongs to.

stateCode.description: The statecode to which the location belongs to.

address.description: Address of the location containing Cityname, Statecode and countrycode respectively.

latitude.description: Latitude of the location on Earth.

longitude.description: Longitude of the location on Earth.

geoCode.description: Geocode of the location containing latitude and longitude respectively.

hotelIds.description: HotelIDs associated with the location only if it's a hotel. For leisure property dupes ID are listed as well.

relevance.description: A no. between 1-100. The higher the number better is the relevant search for that location.

subType.description: The category of the location or Point of reference (HOTEL_LEISURE,HOTEL_GDS).

type.description: Type of resource or the resource name.
